  "title": "PERSONAL ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></u><br /><br />Executive & Calendar Management: Manage and update monthly and daily calendars for the CEO and COO, ensuring all meetings and appointments are scheduled efficiently.</p><p>Corporate Communication & Coordination: Represent the management team in communications with stakeholders, drafting and proofreading correspondence, and recording minutes for management meetings.</p><p>Travel & Event Planning: Coordinate business trips and assist in planning management retreats, ensuring all logistical details are handled seamlessly.</p><p>Claims & Reporting: Process expense claims and prepare monthly reports, ensuring accuracy and timely submission.</p><p>General Support: Provide light housekeeping and assist with personal errands, ensuring the CEO and COO can focus on their key responsibilities.</p><p>Requirements</p><p>Experience: Minimum of 5 years in a PA/EA role or similar executive support position.</p><p>Skills: Proficiency in Microsoft Office, calendar tools, and PowerPoint. Strong communication skills and the ability to multitask and prioritize effectively.</p><p>Attributes: Comfortable with after-hours responsiveness, confidential matters, and able to act quickly under pressure. High emotional intelligence and professional discretion.</p>",
